  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u2018\u0bae\u0bc7\u2019 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "May electricity list is mandatory to buy gas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Gas will be distributed in populated areas including Colombo today (11) and tomorrow (12).",
        "The e-list has been requested to prevent non-essential storage of gas cylinders, Lito has announced."
      ],
